{
  "stem": "26022.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is how I spent the first night, worrying about my mother above all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing I could do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Early up, which is fine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I won't have these skirts hanging over my head anymore when any one of those people needed to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they picked up the straw mattresses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Jehovah's Witness lady flipped back her bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was more space.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was-- which I had not known in the dusk and in the dark-- there was also a table on the other wall flipped up, which was brought down.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And oh, you would say, like, a picnic table and a picnic bench, you know-- two benches alongside the table.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was a place to sit, and a place to-- to lean.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I made myself as thin as I could and slid to the wall and just caught up on my physical strength.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then they brought some soup and some beans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't recall what it-- it was something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was warm.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was in a bowl, and it had a spoon, and I ate it, of course.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And so the days went by.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the conversation never included me, except at one time the Jehovah's Witness lady told me how she had gotten there-- and she told me because she probably told any  one of the others a number of times, so she had a new audience-- that she was doing the wash, and somebody came and took her to where she was now.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so what was happening to the wash?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the wash can't soak forever, and also, the others need the-- the-- the laundry room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they probably threw her wash down on the floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
